RESEARCH ALERT - DeVry price targets raised . - - EVEREN Securiites Inc said Monday it raised its stock price targets for DeVry Inc , the provider of higher education and degrees in technical and business areas , to $ 48 from $ 42 for the period six months from now , and to $ 57 from $ 50 for 18 months out . - - DeVry is well positioned to benefit from higher enrollment rates driven by increasing numbers of high school graduates , higher college participation rates , a curriculum focused on fast growing technology - oriented and business management career education and an enlarging network of campus locations , EVEREN noted in a report . - - DeVry was trading at 47 , up 1 / 8 . - - Chicago newsdesk 312 408 - 8787 
